title: West Palm Beach man accused of fatally shooting toddler during drug deal
text: West Palm Beach man accused of fatally shooting toddler during drug deal WHITE, DEVONTE LAMAR Palm Beach County Sheriff's Office Devonte White, 24, of West Palm Beach, is accused of shooting and killing a toddler during an attempted drug deal robbery.
